<br>
In a nutshell....<br>
<br>
Your friends list is in charactername_##.ini.<br>
Your hotkeys are saved in charactername_##.opt.<br>
<br>
Your global settings, like chat filters, display options, etc. are saved in three files: eqoptions1.opt, eqoptions2.opt, and eqclient.ini.<br>
<br>
